OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778847105
OL,3,CWhich supermarket sells the cheapest
OL,4,Cbranded food?
OL,6,FWhich? found that 240 branded items at
OL,7,FSainsbury's were 17% more expensive
OL,8,Fthan at Asda while Tesco (#912.56) was
OL,9,F15% more, without a loyalty card. Asda
OL,10,Fdoes not offer exclusive prices to its
OL,11,FRewards customers.
OL,13,FThe 240 items, which included Dolmio
OL,14,FBolognese Sauce, Nescafe Azera instant
OL,15,Fcoffee and Mr Kipling Angel Cake
OL,16,FSlices, came to #795.21 at Asda.
OL,26,@vD@Xrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
