OL,3,CWhich supermarket sells the cheapest
OL,4,Cbranded food?
OL,6,FAldi and Lidl are not included in the
OL,7,Fanalysis because they do not stock a
OL,8,Fsufficiently wide range of branded
OL,9,Fgroceries.
OL,11,FA Sainsbury's spokesman said: "All
OL,12,Fexamples in this report were cheaper
OL,13,Fon Nectar Prices and our customers
OL,14,Fknow a good deal when they see one,
OL,15,Fwith 85% of sales involving a Nectar
OL,16,Fcard.
