OL,3,CWhich supermarket sells the cheapest
OL,4,Cbranded food?
OL,6,F"We are committed to delivering
OL,7,Foutstanding value on the products
OL,8,Fpeople buy the most, including over
OL,9,F700 products in the biggest Aldi Price
OL,10,FMatch on the market and our own-brand
OL,11,Fvalue lines."
OL,13,FA Tesco spokesman said: "It's no
OL,14,Fsecret that Clubcard unlocks the
OL,15,Fbiggest savings at Tesco ` but it's
OL,16,Fjust one of the ways our customers get
OL,17,Fgreat value.
